snippet.title: Tank Maniacs - Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
Tank Maniacs is a couch party game with tanks for all those people out there who like couches and tanks. Currently we’re in Closed Beta on PC and we’re looking for an amazing community who would be willing to help us realize our vision for Tank Maniacs by breaking our beta build. And our hearts.  

Don't forget to sign up now for the Closed Beta at www.tankmaniacs.com and join the official Tank Maniacs Discord server at https://discord.gg/PBYT7FR! You can ask the devs there.
